'''Kalifa Dienta''' (yavutse 1 Mutarama 1940), yari umukinnyi wa firime wo muri [[Mali]] .<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0226064/</ref>  Yari azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa filime yakunzwe cyane ''A Banna'' .  Usibye gutanga icyerekezo, yari n'umwanditsi akaba n'umukinnyi wa sinema<ref>https://www.screenweek.it/stars/23656/bio</ref>.<ref>https://letterboxd.com/director/kalifa-dienta/</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 1 Mutarama 1940 i Macina, muri [[Mali]], yitaba Imana ku ya 2021 i Bamako, muri [[Mali]]. Yize sinema i Moscou<ref>https://www.erudit.org/fr/revues/cb/1987-v6-n3-cb1134308/34591ac.pdf</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1980, yayoboye filime ''A Banna'' yakiriwe neza cyane n'abayireba kandi atoranywa mu minsi mikuru mpuzamahanga ya firime.<ref>https://www.imdb.com/search/name/?birth_place=Mali</ref>

